name: Jeem I
description: 3 level map pack meant for gzDoom. May work with zDoom, have not tried it. Jumping is enabled though jumping is not meant to be used, everything can be 100%ed without jumping. Difficulty levels are not implemented either. It is kind of slaughtermap-ish, but it shouldn't be too difficult. Don't fall into acid. This is my first real "map pack", though I have fiddled around with smaller stuff before.
